&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You Will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will report into the Florence Operations team, where you will lead the company-wide AI transformation &amp;amp; integration efforts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively with key Florence functions (GTM, G&amp;amp;A, Product, R&amp;amp;D)&amp;nbsp; to identify the most impactful processes to re-think and automate using AI tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own company-wide AI roadmap aligned to efficiency, product leverage, and ROI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help identify and prioritize use cases (quick wins vs. foundational builds), and deconstruct complex workflows and redesign them with AI embedded (not layered on)&lt;/li&gt;
