&lt;li&gt;Provide support for functional teams with an “AI Enablement Partner” mentality, with targeted support around building the right automation code or scripts and suggesting the right tool set&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build repeatable playbooks for other functions and teams to leverage and get to a faster start, thereby creating a flywheel effect around AI transformation in the company&lt;/li&gt;
