&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Florence software advances cures by helping the world’s most important research sites do their best work. Our solutions are now used by over 30,000 research teams in 70 countries around the world—we’re the most widely deployed site workflow tool in the industry. By the end of the decade, we’ll double the pace at which new medicines get to market by doubling the output of trial site teams.&amp;nbsp;To date, we were named a Deloitte Fast 50 business, G2 Category Leader, an Inc. &amp;amp; AJC best place to work, and an Inc. 5000 company five years in a row.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
